text: Cecilia Buck-Taylor (born December 18, 1953) is an American politician who served in the Connecticut House of Representatives from the 67th district from 2013 to 2017. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Connecticut House of Representatives Category:Connecticut Republicans Category:Women state legislators in Connecticut Category:Politicians from Brooklyn Category:21st-century American politicians Category:21st-century American women politicians
